PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778242270
OL,3,CKeswick indoor centre boss pleads not
OL,4,Cguilty to charges connected to man's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FHe died several days later at the
OL,8,FCumberland Infirmary in Carlisle.
OL,10,FPaul Cornforth, 63, company director
OL,11,Fof Kong Adventure, appeared today at
OL,12,FNewcastle Crown Court charged under
OL,13,Fthe Health and Safety at work act 1974.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778242270
OL,3,CKeswick indoor centre boss pleads not
OL,4,Cguilty to charges connected to man's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FIt is alleged that the company, on or
OL,8,Fbefore 22nd April, 2023, failed to
OL,9,Fconduct its undertaking for the indoor
OL,10,Fcaving experience at Kong Adventure
OL,11,FCentre to ensure people outside its
OL,12,Femployment ` including Mr O'Keeffe `
OL,13,Fwere not exposed to risks to their
OL,14,Fhealth and safety.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778242270
OL,3,CKeswick indoor centre boss pleads not
OL,4,Cguilty to charges connected to man's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FCornforth faces a separate charge of
OL,8,Ffailing to discharge a duty. This
OL,9,Falleges that the company committed an
OL,10,Foffence "with the consent or
OL,11,Fconnivance ` or was attributable to
OL,12,Fthe neglect" ` of Cornforth as an
OL,13,Fofficer of the business.
OL,15,FHe pleaded not guilty to both charges.
OL,17,FA trial date was set for 12th April
OL,18,F2027.
